	<article class="post-81798 post type-post status-publish hentry category-dashboard tag-small-business tag-start-ups tag-united-states-economy des-small-business des-start-ups des-united-states-economy" id="post-81798">
	<header class="postHeader">
				<div class="postKicker">
					</div>
				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Today in Small Business: Name Your Own Price</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Gene Marks			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-01-16T18:14:25+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">January 16, 2014 1:14 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">January 16, 2014 1:14 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/01/16/today-in-small-business-name-your-own-price/" data-title="Today in Small Business: Name Your Own Price" data-description="A new chief of the S.B.A. Federal contracts going to private companies plunge. What business owners wish they had known when they started.">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Washington</b></p>
<ul>
<li>President Obama picks the <a href="//www.nytimes.com/reuters/2014/01/15/business/15reuters-usa-obama-sba.html?">founder</a> of a bank that lends to small businesses to lead the Small Business Administration.</li>
<li>The value of <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/01/16/business/federal-contracts-plunge-squeezing-private-companies.html">federal contracts</a> going to private companies has plunged.</li>
<li><a href="//www.industryweek.com/environment/blown-away-us-suspends-wind-power-subsidies-now">Wind power</a> subsidies have been suspended.</li>
<li>The House <a href="//finance.yahoo.com/news/house-approves-government-wide-1-212209365.html">approves</a> a new spending bill, and Kevin Williamson <a href="//www.realclearpolitics.com/2014/01/15/farewell_sequester_323670.html">laments the demise</a> of the sequestration.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span id="more-81798"></span><br />
<b>The Economy</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="//www.talkingbiznews.com/2/consumer-spending-climbs-in-december/">Consumer spending</a> climbed in December.</li>
<li>A Gallup poll finds that although more Americans are <a href="//www.gallup.com/poll/166850/americans-worse-off-financially-year-ago.aspx?">worse off</a> financially than a year ago, most expect to be better off within a year.</li>
<li>Recent economic <a href="//www.calculatedriskblog.com/2014/01/feds-beige-book-economic-activity.html?">activity increased</a> &#8220;at a moderate pace&#8221; according to the Federal Reserve.</li>
<li><a href="//www.reuters.com/article/2014/01/15/us-usa-economy-prices-idUSBREA0E0TT20140115?f">Producer prices advanced</a> but inflation is still tame.</li>
<li>Weekly <a href="//online.wsj.com/article/BT-CO-20140115-703289.html">mortgage applications</a> surged.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Management</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Here are five businesses that let their customers <a href="//www.fastcompany.com/3024842/bottom-line/inside-five-businesses-that-let-customers-name-their-own-price?">name their own price</a>.</li>
<li>What 15 small-business owners <a href="//www.businessinsider.com/small-business-lessons-learned-2014-1?op=1">wish they had known</a> when they started.</li>
<li>Google has <a href="//mashable.com/2014/01/15/google-acquisitions-17-billion/?">spent more</a> on acquisitions than five rivals combined.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Employees</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="//www.policymic.com/articles/79151/all-of-the-74-000-new-jobs-created-in-december-went-to-women">The 74,000 job gains</a> in December went to women.</li>
<li>These are the <a href="//www.resourcenation.com/blog/the-three-rs-of-small-business-hr/38232/">three Râs</a> of small-business human resources management.</li>
<li><a href="//business.time.com/2014/01/15/strippers-are-winning-the-fight-for-a-minimum-wage/">Strippers are winning</a> the fight for a minimum wage.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Start-Up</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Here are four <a href="//upandrunning.bplans.com/2014/01/15/4-unnecessary-expenses-every-startup-can-live-without/?">expenses</a> every start-up can live without.</li>
<li>Om Malik <a href="https://www.twitter.com/om/status/423234137604882432/photo/1">tweets</a>: &#8220;VC investors have poured in $468M into home automation startups since the start of 2012.&#8221;</li>
<li>Some business owners find that running a home-based business <a href="//www.jdnews.com/news/local/business-owners-home-based-business-allows-them-to-crawl-before-walking-1.262284">allows them to crawl</a> before walking.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Retail</b></p>
<ul>
<li>December <a href="//nrn.com/millerpulse/report-december-restaurant-sales-continue-downward-trend">restaurant sales</a> continued their downward trend according to a survey, and the industry had its worst year for same-store sales since 2009.</li>
<li>J.C. Penney says it <a href="//business.time.com/2014/01/15/jc-penney-is-laying-off-2000-workers/">plans to close</a> 33 stores and lay off 2,000 employees. Jon C. Ogg <a href="//247wallst.com/retail/2014/01/15/j-c-penney-store-closures-likely-just-a-starting-point/?">says</a> the moves are âlikely just a starting point.â</li>
<li>Here are 10 ways to <a href="//www.smallbizdaily.com/14787/10-ways-drive-traffic-ecommerce-store-using-twitter-influencers/">drive traffic</a> to your e-commerce store using Twitter influencers.</li>
<li>More retail businesses are <a href="//online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303453004579290632128929194">using sensors</a> to track their customers and build shopper profiles</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Social Media</b></p>
<ul>
<li>LinkedIn starts a marketplace to <a href="//thenextweb.com/insider/2014/01/15/linkedin-launches-volunteer-marketplace-place-connect-team-charitable-organizations/">connect</a> volunteers with nonprofits.</li>
<li>Here are seven <a href="https://www.openforum.com/articles/7-emerging-social-networks-to-watch-in-2014/">emerging social networks</a> to watch in 2014.</li>
<li>Three million teenagers <a href="//istrategylabs.com/2014/01/3-million-teens-leave-facebook-in-3-years-the-2014-facebook-demographic-report/">have left Facebook</a> in the past three years, according to a new report.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Around the Country</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Dallas-Fort Worth <a href="//www.bizjournals.com/dallas/blog/2014/01/d-fw-small-business-lending-soars-32.html">small-business lending</a> leaps 32 percent.</li>
<li>Sales of <a href="//www.bizjournals.com/philadelphia/morning_roundup/2014/01/exclusive-sales-of-small-businesses.html?ana=e_phil_rdup&amp;s=newsletter&amp;ed=2014-01-16">small businesses in Philadelphia</a> were up 38 percent in 2013.</li>
<li>Wary business owners are <a href="//www.cbsnews.com/news/wary-businesses-reopen-in-charleston-after-hazardous-spill/">reopening</a> in Charleston, W.Va. after the recent hazardous chemical spill.</li>
<li>Businesses <a href="//www.bizpacreview.com/2014/01/14/business-with-gun-free-zone-signs-may-be-tagged-with-legal-liability-94257">with âgun-free zoneâ signs</a> may be tagged with legal liability after a shooting.</li>
<li>Voters in Jackson, Miss., <a href="//www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2014/01/15/jackson-ms-sales-tax-vote/4489851/">approve</a> a 1 percent sales tax.</li>
<li>A âlocal dataâ conference is planned for <a href="//streetfightmag.com/local-data-summit-2014/">Feb. 25</a> in Denver.</li>
<li>A study finds <a href="//www.marketwired.com/press-release/bmo-harris-bank-study-wisconsin-business-owners-feeling-good-about-prospects-their-businesses-1869474.htm">Wisconsin business owners</a> are feeling good about their prospects.</li>
<li>These are the nerdiest, smartest, hardest-working, most exciting and downright best <a href="//www.movoto.com/blog/top-ten/best-cities-in-america-2013/">cities in the country</a>, according to a year of studying what makes Americaâs metropolitan areas so great.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Around the World</b></p>
<ul>
<li>The World Bank <a href="//www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-01-15/world-bank-raises-growth-forecasts-as-richest-nations-strengthen.html">raises its growth forecast</a>.</li>
<li>The Puerto Rican debt crisis is just one of <a href="//seekingalpha.com/article/1946741-five-major-underreported-economic-threats?">five under-reported</a> economic threats, according to one blogger.</li>
<li><a href="//www.businessinsider.com/somali-piracy-crackdown-2014-1">Piracy at sea</a> is at a six-year low.</li>
<li>Scores of factories in China&#8217;s manufacturing heartlands <a href="//www.reuters.com/article/2014/01/15/us-china-migration-idUSBREA0E1K920140115?">have closed earlier</a> than usual for the country&#8217;s biggest holiday because the outlook is grim.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Health Care</b></p>
<ul>
<li>âOver time, this will work out,â <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2014/01/15/over-time-this-will-work-out-wellpoint-ceo-joe-swedish-on-obamacare/">says</a> the chief executive of Wellpoint.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Technology</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Hewlett-Packard is <a href="//www.siliconbeat.com/2014/01/15/hewlett-packard-re-enters-smartphone-business/">re-entering</a> the smartphone business.</li>
<li>Microsoft decides to <a href="//thenextweb.com/microsoft/2014/01/15/microsoft-extends-updates-windows-xp-security-products-july-14-2015/#!">extend its updates</a> for Windows XP security products until July 14, 2015.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><em>Gene Marks owns the Marks Group, a Bala Cynwyd, Pa., consulting firm that helps clients with customer relationship management. You can follow him on <a href="https://www.twitter.com/genemarks">Twitter</a>.</em></p>
